---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Upstream Lens">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <section>
    <h2>What is Upstream Lens</h2>
    <p>
      Upstream Lens is an <strong>unofficial, individually-operated analytical media</strong> that analyzes discussions, design philosophies, and structural changes in open source upstream communities, organizing and sharing them in a format useful for enterprise and platform engineers to make informed decisions.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Position</h2>
    <p>
      This site clarifies the following positions:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>This is an <strong>unofficial, individually-operated site</strong> not affiliated with any specific foundation or organization</li>
      <li>We <strong>explicitly state our perspective</strong> without pretending neutrality</li>
      <li>We focus on <strong>decision-making structures</strong>, not just technology choices</li>
      <li>We <strong>provide thinking frameworks</strong>, not tool comparisons</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Target Audience</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Platform Engineers</li>
      <li>Enterprise / Cloud Architects</li>
      <li>Engineers interested in OSS community structures</li>
      <li>Leads and managers involved in technology selection and standardization</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>What This Site Does NOT Provide</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Beginner tutorials or hands-on guides</li>
      <li>How-to guides for individual tools</li>
      <li>Tool comparison rankings</li>
      <li>News or breaking updates</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
